the explanation of the four feet\nof Brahman, as first mentioned in III, 18, x. Each foot or quarter of Brahman\nis represented as fourfold, and the knowledge of these sixteen parts is called\nthe Sho _d_ a _s_ akalavidya.\n\n* * *\n\n[Next: IV, 5](sbe01082.htm)\n\n'